features: Personalized Canvas Prints: Choose the size and template you like, and upload your picture. We will customize canvas prints based on your photos. Customized personalized collage picture can save a special moment on exquisite canvas.

Premium Canvas Poster: Fine workmanship and materials are the guarantee of quality. The personalized printed image is full of sharp and vitality color, you can clearly see every detail on the picture. Use archive ink, bright and colorful, environmentally friendly, waterproof, anti-ultraviolet, and never fade!

Ready to Hang: There is a metal hook on the back of our personalized photos, which can be hung at anytime. It is suitable for the space of the family, living room, bedroom, bathroom, dining room, kitchen or any area in the home.

Note: Click the "Customize Now" button to add image to the specified box. When uploading the photo, please make sure that the photo covers the entire canvas area, and select the template size that match photo. Please upload the picture in the "JPEG" file format. (P.S. Do not use mobile phone screenshots because they are of lower quality, and low-resolution pictures will be low-quality prints.)

Personalized Gift: A special personalized gift is a good choice for your wife, husband, parents, grandparents, partner, friends or girlfriends, especially suitable for important occasions such as weddings, Thanksgiving, Christmas, Father's Day, Valentine's Day, birthday decorations, etc.
description: ● This custom canvas is more than an ordinary canvas printed poster. Custom wall photos are your own original artwork with stunning painting textures and great collection value! ● In life, there is a precious story and memory behind every photo. Through different forms of display, you can clearly know your growth. ● A small customized poster can change one's living environment and carry the memories of the family's warm life. It can reflect people's heart desires, longing for warmth, memories and romance. ● Best gift for your family and friend on Christmas, Wedding, Anniversary, Thanksgiving, Christmas, Mother's Day, Father's Day, Valentine, Birthday, etc.
